room_title: Escape room "Detention" by Kuma Escape in San Jose
room_address: 3777 Stevens Creek Blvd. #340 Santa Clara, CA 95051
room_description: Today is your high school senior trip! You and your friends have been looking forward to this all year, but unfortunately, you are all stuck in detention. The bus for the airport leaves in an hour; can you escape detention and make it in time?
